      "name": "DaSt-2026: Road Safety Analysis \u2014 Accident-Severity Classification (North Yorkshire, 2009\u20132013)",
      "description": "FAIR-compliant ML experiment for the DaSt 2026 course at TU Wien. Predicts road-accident severity (fatal / serious / slight) from UK STATS19 records for North Yorkshire (2009\u20132013). Data is re-published in 3NF on the TU Wien DBRepo test instance and loaded into the experiment exclusively via the DBRepo REST API. The trained model and its FAIR4ML metadata are deposited on the TU Wien Research Data Repository (test instance); the source code and full metadata package are released on GitHub and Zenodo.",
